h generation, Neapolitan families. One teaching the oven and the other pizza Napoletana.\" In addition to our Neapolitan pizza we have a variety of home-made pastas, soups and desserts which are made fresh on location and from scratch. Our ingredients are either imported from Italy or locally grown and organic.", photoCount: "152.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 15, \"count2\": 16, \"count3\": 31, \"count4\": 67, \"count5\": 260}", email: "tampa@bavarospizza.com", website: "https://bavarospizza.com/locations/tampa/", rankingPosition: "12.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 720, \"openHours\": \"12:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}]], \"timezone\": \"America/New_York\"}", address: "514 North Franklin Street #101, Tampa, FL 33602", neighborhoodLocations: [], dishes: ["Pasta", "Salad", "Cannoli", "Tiramisu", "Prosciutto", "Meatballs", "Tagliatelle", "Bolognese", "Gelato", "Antipasti", "Margherita Pizza", "Pesto", "Penne", "Wood Fired Pizza", "Soup", "Homemade Pasta", "Rigatoni", "Sausage", "Fresh Pasta", "Pies"], reviewTags: "[{\"text\": \"pizza\", \"reviews\": 165}, {\"text\": \"ravioli\", \"reviews\": 26}, {\"text\": \"cannoli\", \"reviews\": 14}, {\"text\": \"garlic bread\", \"reviews\": 8}, {\"text\": \"antipasti\", \"reviews\": 9}, {\"text\": \"fresh pasta\", \"reviews\": 4}, {\"text\": \"pie\", \"reviews\": 6}, {\"text\": \"brick oven\", \"reviews\": 11}, {\"text\": \"vodka sauce\", \"reviews\": 9}, {\"text\": \"dow